               <p>I am a waiter at the <placeName id="t17881022-7-crimeloc31">London coffee-house</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17881022-7-crimeloc31" type="placeName" value="London coffee-house"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17881022-7-crimeloc31" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881022-7-off29 t17881022-7-crimeloc31"></join>, which is kept by Mr. Rowley and Mr. Leach; on the 25th of September, the prisoner and another man came in, and called for two basons of soup when they went out, I missed a silver spoon; I followed the prisoner, and took the spoon out of his pocket, and dragged him back into the coffee-room.</p>
               <p>(The spoon produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>The waiter followed me, and put the spoon in my pocket, and took me back, and then took it out of my pocket; I knew nothing of it.</p>
